{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Node commands</h1>\n<h2>Add node</h2>\n<p><strong>Command: <code class=\"language-text\">addnode &lt;name&gt;</code></strong></p>\n<p>Add a new empty node to a cluster.</p>\n<p><strong>Options</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--types</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-t</code> (required) - The node type(s) to choose between <code class=\"language-text\">master</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">sidemaster</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">edge</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">worker</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">ldap</code>. Type <code class=\"language-text\">-t</code> before each type. See <a href=\"../getting-started/key-principles.md\">Key principles</a> for type descriptions and <a href=\"../advanced-usage.md\">Avanced usage</a> for custom type creation.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--ip</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-i</code> (prompt if not specified) - The node IP address.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--ram</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-r</code> (prompt if not specified) - The memory allocated to the node in MB.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--cpus</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-p</code> - The number of CPUs allocated to the node, 1 by default.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--cluster</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-c</code> - The cluster to which the node should be added.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>List nodes</h2>\n<p><strong>Command: <code class=\"language-text\">listnodes</code></strong></p>\n<p>List the nodes of a cluster.</p>\n<p><strong>Options</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--cluster</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-c</code> - The cluster on which to list the nodes.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Remove node</h2>\n<p><strong>Command: <code class=\"language-text\">rmnode &lt;name&gt;</code></strong></p>\n<p>Remove a node from a cluster.</p>\n<p><strong>Options</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--force</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-f</code> - Avoid the confirmation prompt.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--cluster</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">-c</code> - The cluster in which the node should be deleted.</li>\n</ul>","id":"ffadc381-86a0-5b02-a1d0-354d4e191d8e","frontmatter":{"title":"Node commands"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"84b64b39-9c4a-5b08-958b-fda2c3b9b93f","frontmatter":{"title":"Overview","sort":1},"fields":{"slug":"docs"}}},{"node":{"id":"be7a7cec-43f8-539b-8eb4-ef9e61f6571a","frontmatter":{"title":"Cluster commands","sort":2},"fields":{"slug":"docs/commands/cluster"}}},{"node":{"id":"22c8d060-e9bf-55b3-8c14-4f20be9cd230","frontmatter":{"title":"Key principles","sort":2},"fields":{"slug":"docs/getting-started/key-principles"}}},{"node":{"id":"dfacebff-7d12-5d9e-a6a0-904de2d228b8","frontmatter":{"title":"Getting started","sort":2},"fields":{"slug":"docs/getting-started"}}},{"node":{"id":"ffadc381-86a0-5b02-a1d0-354d4e191d8e","frontmatter":{"title":"Node commands","sort":3},"fields":{"slug":"docs/commands/node"}}},{"node":{"id":"6d3e5922-3975-51c1-823f-ed8fe22aa362","frontmatter":{"title":"Service commands","sort":3},"fields":{"slug":"docs/commands/service"}}},{"node":{"id":"14c1e223-d215-5831-8845-215e25c3be84","frontmatter":{"title":"Installation","sort":3},"fields":{"slug":"docs/getting-started/installation"}}},{"node":{"id":"18643e17-c7d3-58fb-899f-85a55637ce16","frontmatter":{"title":"Jumbo CLI","sort":3},"fields":{"slug":"docs/commands"}}},{"node":{"id":"6dca226f-2ed7-547f-aa41-e0b79b358812","frontmatter":{"title":"Cluster configuration","sort":4},"fields":{"slug":"docs/getting-started/configuration"}}},{"node":{"id":"c8eb77f0-d4d3-5d56-8715-ed9680c556de","frontmatter":{"title":"Advanced usage","sort":4},"fields":{"slug":"docs/advanced-usage"}}},{"node":{"id":"4a8a9459-ae42-5bbf-b405-7d814764041a","frontmatter":{"title":"Component commands","sort":5},"fie